{"title":"C语言程序汇总","date":"2020-05-04T12:05:29.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"May 4, 2020","L":"05/04/2020","MM-DD":"05-04"},"link":"2020/05/04/C语言程序汇总","comments":true,"tags":["C语言程序汇总"],"categories":["C语言","笔记"],"updated":"2020-05-21T03:03:00.225Z","content":"<h2 id=\"三角形\">三角形<a href=\"#三角形\" title=\"三角形\"></a></h2><ol><li><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">main()</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    int a,b,c;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    for(a&#x3D;1;a&lt;6;a++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;\tfor(b&#x3D;5;b&gt;&#x3D;a*2-a;b--)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            printf(&quot; &quot;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        for(b&#x3D;1;b&lt;&#x3D;a*2-1;b++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            printf(&quot;*&quot;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        printf(&quot;\\n&quot;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure> 输出结果：<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">    *</span><br><span class=\"line\">   ***</span><br><span class=\"line\">  *****</span><br><span class=\"line\"> *******</span><br><span class=\"line\">*********</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ol><h2 id=\"对用户输入的任意一组数字，如2343527834输出其中出现次数最多的数及次数\">对用户输入的任意一组数字，如{2,3,4,3,5,2,7,8,3,4}输出其中出现次数最多的数及次数<a href=\"#对用户输入的任意一组数字，如2343527834输出其中出现次数最多的数及次数\" title=\"对用户输入的任意一组数字，如{2,3,4,3,5,2,7,8,3,4}输出其中出现次数最多的数及次数\"></a></h2><ol><li><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">#include&lt;math.h&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">#include&lt;stdlib.h&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">#include&lt;string.h&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">int main()</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    int i,j,n,max,a[1010],b[1010]&#x3D;&#123;&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    printf(&quot;要输入多少个数？&quot;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    scanf(&quot;%d&quot;,&amp;n);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    printf(&quot;请输入&quot;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    for(i&#x3D;0;i&lt;n;i++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        scanf(&quot;%d&quot;,&amp;a[i]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    for(i&#x3D;0;i&lt;n;i++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        for(j&#x3D;0;j&lt;n;j++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            if(a[i]&#x3D;&#x3D;a[j])</span><br><span class=\"line\">                b[i]++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    max&#x3D;b[0],j&#x3D;0;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    for(i&#x3D;0;i&lt;n;i++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        if(b[i]&gt;max)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            max&#x3D;b[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            j&#x3D;i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    printf(&quot;重复值%d 数量%d\\n&quot;,a[j],max);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    return 0;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"字符串多组输入，直到遇到回车结束输入\"><mark><strong>字符串多组输入，直到遇到回车结束输入</strong></mark><a href=\"#字符串多组输入，直到遇到回车结束输入\" title=\"字符串多组输入，直到遇到回车结束输入\"></a></h2><p>论他大神给出的解决办法</p>\n</li>\n<li><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"> string s;</span><br><span class=\"line\">while(getline(std::cin,s)&amp;&amp;!s.empty())&#123;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">   char s[maxn];</span><br><span class=\"line\">while(gets(s)&amp;&amp;strcmp(s,&quot;&quot;)!&#x3D;0)&#123;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ol>","prev":{"title":"Hello World","link":"2020/05/24/hello-world"},"plink":"https://dxsummer.gitee.io/2020/05/04/C语言程序汇总/","toc":[{"id":"三角形","title":"三角形","index":"1"},{"id":"对用户输入的任意一组数字，如2343527834输出其中出现次数最多的数及次数","title":"对用户输入的任意一组数字，如{2,3,4,3,5,2,7,8,3,4}输出其中出现次数最多的数及次数","index":"2"},{"id":"字符串多组输入，直到遇到回车结束输入","title":"字符串多组输入，直